A man is critical after he was stabbed multiple times in Spartan, Kempton Park on Thursday.It is reported that the man s girlfriend was also assaulted.ER24 Spokesperson Ineke van Huyssteen said &#8220;when ER24 paramedics arrived on scene, the man was lying on the side of the road. Bystanders were tending to him&#8221;.He added &#8220;ER24 assessed the man and the woman s injuries. The man had a serious stab wound to his arm as well as below his neck&#8221;.Both of them were transported to Tembisa hospital.-TNA Reporter 